gel1Lane1 = "A1	B1	C1	D1	E1	F1	G1	H1	A2	B2	C2	D2	E2	F2	G2	H2".split("\t")
gel1Lane1 = "  ".join(gel1Lane1)

gel1Lane2 = "A3	B3	C3	D3	E3	F3	G3	H3	A4	B4	C4	D4	E4	F4	G4	H4".split("\t")
gel1Lane2 = "  ".join(gel1Lane2)

gel1Lane3 = "A5	B5	C5	D5	E5	F5	G5	H5	A6	B6	C6	D6	E6	F6	G6	H6".split("\t")
gel1Lane3 = "  ".join(gel1Lane3)

plt.figure(figsize=(16,8))
plt.subplot(121)
plt.imshow(img.imread('gels/1_1_Lecture 2022-02-01_16h25m40s.tif'))
plt.title('First 48 pool 1')
plt.text(35, 50, gel1Lane1, color='white', )
plt.text(35, 220, gel1Lane2, color='white', )
plt.text(35, 400, gel1Lane3, color='white', )
plt.subplot(122)
plt.imshow(img.imread('gels/2_1_Lecture 2022-02-02_14h24m29s.tif'))
plt.title('First 48 pool 2, forgot marker and got distracted')
plt.text(32, 110, gel1Lane1, color='white', )
plt.text(32, 280, gel1Lane2, color='white', )
plt.text(30, 455, gel1Lane3, color='white', )

plt.show()

nextDf = pd.read_csv('gisaid/nextclade.csv', sep = ";")
keep = ['seqName', 'clade', 'qc.overallScore', 'qc.overallStatus','missing', 'totalMissing',
        'qc.privateMutations.status', 'qc.missingData.status','qc.mixedSites.status',
       'qc.snpClusters.status']
nextDf = nextDf[keep]
In [6]:
for thing in ['qc.overallStatus', 
              'qc.privateMutations.status',
              'qc.missingData.status',
              'qc.mixedSites.status',
              'qc.snpClusters.status']:
    plt.figure(figsize=(6,3))
    sns.countplot(data=nextDf, x='clade', hue=thing, dodge=True,
                 palette={'good': 'cornflowerblue', 
                          'mediocre': 'gray', 
                          'bad': 'black'})
    plt.legend(bbox_to_anchor=(1, 1), loc=2)
    plt.title(f"{thing} of UFS ONT sequencing");
